style: table.GeneratedTable{background-color:#EEE;text-align:left;border-collapse:collapse}table.GeneratedTable td,table.GeneratedTable th{padding:5px 2px}table.GeneratedTable tbody td{font-size:14px;font-weight:700}table.GeneratedTable tr:nth-child(even){background:#DEDEDE}table.GeneratedTable thead{background:#1C6EA4;background:-moz-linear-gradient(top,#5592bb 0%,#327cad 66%,#1C6EA4 100%);background:-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#5592bb 0%,#327cad 66%,#1C6EA4 100%);background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#5592bb 0%,#327cad 66%,#1C6EA4 100%);border-bottom:2px solid #444}table.GeneratedTable thead th{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#FFF;border-left:2px solid #D0E4F5}table.GeneratedTable thead th:first-child{border-left:none}table.GeneratedTable tfoot{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#FFF;background:#D0E4F5;background:-moz-linear-gradient(top,#dcebf7 0%,#d4e6f6 66%,#D0E4F5 100%);background:-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#dcebf7 0%,#d4e6f6 66%,#D0E4F5 100%);background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#dcebf7 0%,#d4e6f6 66%,#D0E4F5 100%);border-top:2px solid #444}table.GeneratedTable tfoot td{font-size:14px}table.GeneratedTable tfoot .links{text-align:right}table.GeneratedTable tfoot .links a{display:inline-block;background:#1C6EA4;color:#FFF;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:5px}
